    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place" rend="right">Camden<ptr target="prc.00063_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1877-01-02" rend="right">Tuesday noon Jan 2<ptr target="prc.00063_n2"/></date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>

            <p>The snow is so heavy &#38; the ferry obstructed so by ice I defer my coming for a day or two.<ptr target="prc.00063_n3"/> I am feeling pretty well &#38; will come soon&#8212;(I won't trouble you to come over for me)</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">WW</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
